name: Samuel Gonzalez
values: Honesty, hard work, and respect for diversity
summary:
Samuel Gonzalez is a 29-year-old straight man from San Antonio, Texas, now residing in Los Angeles, California. He is Hispanic/Latino and identifies himself with he/him/his pronouns. Samuel works as a Project Manager in the Media industry and has a Graduate degree from the University of Chicago. An active individual, he enjoys reading, cooking, hiking, and football. Samuel is an atheist with liberal political views, and values honesty, hard work, and respect for diversity. He's a Sagittarius and an ENTJ personality type who occasionally enjoys a drink, doesn't smoke, or do drugs.

Samuel seeks a straight woman between 25 and 35 years old, who is active and shares his vision of a monogamous relationship. She should also ideally not have children, but like Samuel, be open to having children in the future. He prefers a partner who enjoys a drink but refrains from smoking and drug use.
